casebody.data:
LOUISIANA BOARD OF ETHICS
v.
Susan THEALL Louisiana Board of Ethics
v.
Burton Zaunbrecher 2017-CC-2015 Supreme Court of Louisiana. February 9, 2018 ON WRIT OF CERTIORARI TO THE COURT OF APPEAL, FIRST CIRCUIT, PARISH OF EAST BATON ROUGE Writ denied. Hughes, J., dissents.

I respectfully dissent and would grant the writ. The alleged violation here was not "contained in a report" and is subject to a three year prescriptive period.
